</div>
</ng-template>
Summary & What’s Next
By building on our base overlay infrastructure, we implemented a connected tooltip system that:

• Handles viewport edges dynamically via FlexibleConnectedPositionStrategy.

• Syncs CDK position changes directly into container-level Angular Signals.

• Operates without legacy @HostBinding declarations.

• Supports both string labels and complex TemplateRef views seamlessly.
In Part 5, we will explore building dynamic contextual Context Menus and Dropdown Selects with accessibility and keyboard navigation.
